e month of whole family home quarantine, we all went for testing again on 28 September 2020. With Lord Jagannath's grace, all of us got tested -ve. It was a huge relief as we were cured, and we didn't have any new cases in the family."), mdx("p", null, "So, coming to the main reason for writing this post. We had to follow a lot of rules after we got tested +ve, various from food to living and daily habits. I want to share them as someone might find it useful."), mdx("p", null, mdx("strong", {
